OVERVIEW

  dskill is a tool to KILL .DS_Store!

INSTALL

    $ make install

  this will build and install the `dskill` binary to /usr/local/bin

USAGE

    $ dskill kill

  remove all .DS_Store recursively under current directory

    $ dskill guard

  start a process to prevent creation of .DS_Store recursively under current
  directory

    $ dskill service start

  start a launchd service to always run `dskill guard` on root / directory
  in the background, completely deny any existence of .DS_Store
